mg_sky_climb

It`s an enormous "Climb" map which contains 13 "Jail-Break" maps!

Here is the list of them:

⚡ ba_jail_encore_fix2_centrl

⚡ ba_jail_fridej

⚡ jb_8bit_v8

⚡ jb_gp_among_us_2

⚡ jb_lost_planet_redux_v1

⚡ jb_minecraft_z_v5e

⚡ jb_mlcastle_refurbished_v3

⚡ jb_moonjail_v2

⚡ jb_moti2

⚡ jb_office_beta2-1f_f

⚡ jb_overcooked

⚡ jb_prison_architect_v2

⚡ jb_vanilla_v3

There is also a special "Crazy" level on the map which runs apart from others.

Watch the video to understand which part of the climb matches to any map from the list.

The main parkour consists of 4 difficulty levels:

- Easy

- Normal

- Hard

- Demon

They differ in the number of checkpoints:

- Easy - 8

- Normal - 4

- Hard - 2

- Demon - 0

Each checkpoint color corresponds to the selected difficulty level.

Each checkpoint gives a certain number of TAB-points.

You can play both on MG-version and on JB-version to determine the best parkourists of your server!
